## Common misdiagnoses

| Symptom | Often deployment — not code |
|---------|----------------------------|
| New route 404 | API not rebuilt |
| Old UI after merge | PM2 not restarted / browser cache |
| All users logged out | JWT_SECRET changed |
| `/ready` false | Missing Telnyx key, Redis, or DB |
| Diagnostics 404 | Web not deployed |
| One-way audio at office only | Firewall/TURN — compare WebRTC diagnostics |

Do not modify protected telephony files until deployment is ruled out (see `vsp-phone-development.mdc`).
